### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
### USERS
### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

### List all user profiles (admin use)
GET {{baseUrl}}/users

###

### Get a single user profile by ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/users/{{userId}}

###

### Create a user profile with Supabase auth (testing/seed — prefer /auth/signup)
POST {{baseUrl}}/users
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "full_name": "Test Customer",
  "phone": "0311-9876543",
  "email": "customer@test.com",
  "home_area": "DHA"
}

###

### Update a user profile
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/users/{{userId}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "home_area": "Clifton",
  "phone": "0333-1234567"
}

###

### Delete a user profile
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/users/{{userId}}

###
### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
### ADMIN  (all routes require Authorization)
### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

### Get all platform config values
### Keys: platform_fee_fixed | platform_fee_percent | visit_fee |
###       urgency_fee_high | urgency_fee_medium | loyalty_discount_cap
GET {{baseUrl}}/admin/platform-config
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Update platform_fee_fixed (flat PKR fee per booking)
PUT {{baseUrl}}/admin/platform-config/platform_fee_fixed
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "value": "100"
}

###

### Update platform_fee_percent (% of service subtotal)
PUT {{baseUrl}}/admin/platform-config/platform_fee_percent
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "value": "5.5"
}

###

### Update visit_fee (provider callout/visit fee)
PUT {{baseUrl}}/admin/platform-config/visit_fee
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "value": "200"
}

###

### Update urgency_fee_high (same-day emergency surcharge)
PUT {{baseUrl}}/admin/platform-config/urgency_fee_high
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "value": "500"
}

###

### Update urgency_fee_medium (medium urgency surcharge)
PUT {{baseUrl}}/admin/platform-config/urgency_fee_medium
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "value": "250"
}

###

### Update loyalty_discount_cap (max loyalty discount per booking)
PUT {{baseUrl}}/admin/platform-config/loyalty_discount_cap
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "value": "150"
}
